1148
01:10:40,283 --> 01:10:41,773
No, no. I don't think we do.

1149
01:10:41,951 --> 01:10:44,181
Honestly, if she wants to dance,
let her dance.

1150
01:10:44,353 --> 01:10:47,413
I don't understand. Wait. I'm sorry.
I don't understand.

1151
01:10:47,590 --> 01:10:51,890
Your heroes, the Beatles, Smokey,
they would never let this happen.

1152
01:10:52,061 --> 01:10:54,621
That's a completely different thing.
They were geniuses.

1153
01:10:54,797 --> 01:10:57,391
They wrote dinner. I write dessert.

1154
01:10:57,566 --> 01:10:59,397
No. You're better than dessert.

1155
01:10:59,568 --> 01:11:02,128
That's why I'm gonna tell her
what I think at the party.

1156
01:11:02,305 --> 01:11:04,068
- You are not gonna do that.
- Yes, I am.

1157
01:11:04,240 --> 01:11:05,537
- No, you are not.
- Yes, I am.

1158
01:11:05,708 --> 01:11:07,801
In that case, you are no longer invited.

1159
01:11:07,977 --> 01:11:10,275
What? She invited me.

1160
01:11:10,446 --> 01:11:11,936
She invited us, as a team.

1161
01:11:12,114 --> 01:11:14,878
Now that we disagree,
we no longer present a united front...

1162
01:11:15,051 --> 01:11:17,849
